text: Bokor is a Hungarian surname that may refer to *Elemér Bokor (1887–1928), Hungarian entomologist *Jozsef Bokor, Hungarian scientist *Marián Bokor (born 1977), Slovakian javelin thrower *Margit Bokor (1903?–1949), Hungarian soprano *Pál Bokor (born 1942), Hungarian journalist, writer and translator Category:Hungarian-language surnames
